{
  "doc_id": "26272",
  "text": "HTN is very complex, and both environmental and genetic factors are involved. Yet, it is linked to overweight and obesity in several ways [CITATION_1] . Several epidemiological studies have revealed a strong relationship between obesity and HTN, but there is still controversy regarding the best obesity indicator for HTN and the most appropriate cut-off point to use [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
